001package ltd.icecold.orangeengine.api.event;
002
003import org.bukkit.event.Event;
004import org.bukkit.event.HandlerList;
005
006import java.util.List;
007
008/**
009 * 解析模型完成
010 */
011public class ParseModelFileEvent extends Event {
012    private List<String> parseModelNameList;
013    private static final HandlerList handlers = new HandlerList();
014
015    public ParseModelFileEvent(List<String> parseModelNameList) {
016        this.parseModelNameList = parseModelNameList;
017    }
018
019    public List<String> getParseModelNameList() {
020        return parseModelNameList;
021    }
022
023    @Override
024    public HandlerList getHandlers() {
025        return handlers;
026    }
027
028    public static HandlerList getHandlerList() {
029        return handlers;
030    }
031}
